title: #92Noon Friday Football Feast!
description: PA & Charch in studio for the pre-Super Bowl feast! Pats vox Bob Socci, former Seahawk and SB-winner Cliff Avril courtesy of KJR radio and then Action Network's Chris Raybon all join to help analyze SB LIII. Final hour is heavy on PropBets.
